com.software.reuze

Class d_MapRomaniaRoadsSimplified

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.software.reuze.d_MapExtendable
      • com.software.reuze.d_MapRomaniaRoadsSimplified
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    d_i_Map

    public class d_MapRomaniaRoadsSimplified
extends d_MapExtendable
    Represents a simplified road map of Romania. The initialization method is declared static. So it can also be used to initialize other specialized subclasses of d_MapExtendable with road map data from Romania. Location names, road distances and directions have been extracted from Artificial Intelligence A Modern Approach (2nd Edition), Figure 3.2, page 63. The straight-line distances to Bucharest have been taken from Artificial Intelligence A Modern Approach (2nd Edition), Figure 4.1, page 95.
    Author:
    Ruediger Lunde
